review.reviewBody: Pizza is always well made here. Good ratio of toppings, good amount of cheese.
The pizza was good but I ordered a 2 litre coke and they sent me a single can.
garlic bread was over toasted and they were burned.
This is how my pizza arrived! Totally unacceptable! Also, I ordered cheesy bread but instead they sent garlic bread.
